df_zones = pd.read_csv('taxi+_zone_lookup.csv')

idtozone = dict(zip(df_zones.LocationID.values.tolist(),df_zones.Zone.values.tolist()))
idtoborough = dict(zip(df_zones.LocationID.values.tolist(),df_zones.Borough.values.tolist()))

df['PUzone'] = df['PULocationID'].replace(idtozone)
df['DOzone'] = df['DOLocationID'].replace(idtozone)

df['PUborough'] = df['PULocationID'].replace(idtoborough)
df['DOborough'] = df['DOLocationID'].replace(idtoborough)

In [6]:
df['rev'] = df[['fare_amount','extra','tip_amount']].sum(axis=1)
df.tpep_pickup_datetime = pd.to_datetime(df.tpep_pickup_datetime)
df.tpep_dropoff_datetime = pd.to_datetime(df.tpep_dropoff_datetime)
df['pickup_hour'] = df.tpep_pickup_datetime.apply(lambda x: x.replace(minute=0, second=0))
df['dropoff_hour'] = df.tpep_dropoff_datetime.apply(lambda x: x.replace(minute=0, second=0))
df['pickup_weekday'] = df.tpep_pickup_datetime.apply(lambda x: x.weekday())
df['pickup_dayhour'] = df.tpep_pickup_datetime.apply(lambda x: x.hour)
df['revpermi'] = df.rev/df.trip_distance
In [7]:
df['triptime'] = df.tpep_dropoff_datetime - df.tpep_pickup_datetime
df['triptime'] = df.triptime.astype('timedelta64[s]')/60 # convert to minutes

df['revpermin'] = df.rev/df.triptime
df['revpermi'] = df.rev/df.trip_distance # revenue per mile

In [11]:
# Removing what appears to be bad data
df = df[(df.rev<=200) & (df.rev>0) & (df.trip_distance>0) & (df.trip_distance<100)]

# only keep trips greater than a minute. shorter trips seem unrealistic
df = df[df.triptime>1]

# throw out if pickup time = dropoff (not too many - only removing 9k out of 9million)
df = df[df.tpep_pickup_datetime!=df.tpep_dropoff_datetime]
